    "name": "The Quintessential Quintuplets OMOIDE VR ~YOTSUBA~",
    "steam_appid": 2233020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– About the Game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our time together...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Quintessential Quintuplets OMOIDE VR ~YOTSUBA~ is the second official VR adventure game based on the popular manga series! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Futaro Uesugi and enjoy spending time with the fourth Nakano Quint, Yotsuba, in this VR adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get closer to Yotsuba by experiencing Futaro's daily life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[All Your Favorite Scenes From the Manga Recreated in VR]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a selection of scenes from the manga recreated in fully-voiced VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to listen out for all your favorite lines as you interact with Yotsuba.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Experience Daily Life With Yotsuba]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get closer than ever using VR.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make memories with Yotsuba and watch as she does her signature smile before your very eyes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Multiple Dialogue Options &amp; Endings]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select from a variety of dialogue options as you play through the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep Yotsuba in mind and choose carefully to get the best ending!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– Featured Characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yotsuba Nakano (Voiced by Ayane Sakura)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Futaro Uesugi (Played by you!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >©Negi Haruba / Kodansha Ltd.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >©NextNinja Co.,Ltd.</p>",
